Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這粗獷的碰撞聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這做什麼啊
