Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壓氣機的聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也好這口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朋友裡有個叫森田的鐵道迷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒錯  你是長沼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  都知事選舉請加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很認真很棒喔  超喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝  我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:00:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會吧民眾的心聲融入到政治中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（至  星宮遙）
